      "content": "i hear u, but it feels like u're saying one side is just plain wrong. if the \"consensus\" is that it doesn't work, then does that mean anyone who supports these laws is just ignoring the facts? or is there a legitimate reason why people still want them instead of just focusing on social programs?",
